# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:155
msgid "Previous Versions"
msgstr "历史版本"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:157
msgid ""
"To download old versions of OpenShot Video Editor, you can visit "
"https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tags. Click on the version number "
"you need, and scroll to the bottom, under the release notes. You will find "
"download links for each operating system. Download the appropriate version "
"for your computer, and follow the installation instructions above."
msgstr ""
"要下载 OpenShot 视频编辑器的旧版本，您可以访问 https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-"
"qt/tags。点击所需的版本号，滚动到发布说明底部，您将找到各操作系统的下载链接。下载适合您电脑的版本，并按照上述安装说明操作。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:162
msgid ""
"NOTE: Projects (\\*.osp) made with newer versions of OpenShot Video Editor "
"might not support older versions."
msgstr "注意：使用较新版本 OpenShot Video Editor 创建的项目（\\*.osp）可能不支持较旧版本。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:165
msgid "Uninstall"
msgstr "卸载"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../installation.rst:167
msgid ""
"To fully uninstall OpenShot from your system, you must **manually delete** "
"the ``.openshot_qt`` folder: ``~/.openshot_qt/`` or "
"``C:\\Users\\USERNAME\\.openshot_qt\\``, which contains all settings and "
"files used by OpenShot. Be sure to **backup** any recovery files of your "
"existing projects first (\\*.osp files). Please see "
":ref:`preferences_reset_ref` for instructions on clearing the previous "
"``openshot.settings`` file (for a clean install with **default "
"preferences**)."
msgstr ""
"要完全卸载 OpenShot，您必须**手动删除**``.openshot_qt`` 文件夹：``~/.openshot_qt/`` 或 "
"``C:\\Users\\USERNAME\\.openshot_qt\\`` ，该文件夹包含 OpenShot 使用的所有设置和文件。请务必先** "
"备份**现有项目的任何恢复文件（\\*.osp 文件）。有关清除之前的 ``openshot.settings`` 文件（以进行**默认首选项** "
"的全新安装）的说明，请参见 :ref:`preferences_reset_ref` 。"

